// A 2/2 vanilla carrying ONLY Exalted ([CR#702.83a]) — "Whenever a creature
// you control attacks alone, that creature gets +1/+1 until end of turn." No
// card in the canon corpus has Exalted, so this minimal carrier isolates the
// keyword's trigger RESOLUTION: the lone attacker must bind as `EventObject`
// (the event-provenance the engine derives for an `Attacking` fact) so the
// `Continuously(Modify(of: Of(EventObject)))` pump lands on it.
Normal(
    name: "Exalted Creature",
    mana_cost: [Generic(1), White],
    types: [Creature],
    power: 2,
    toughness: 2,
    abilities: [Keyword(Exalted)],
)
